## Testing Checklist

### Manual Testing

- [ ] **Login Flow**
  - [ ] Login with valid credentials
  - [ ] Redirected to dashboard (no redirect loop)
  - [ ] Token saved in localStorage (check DevTools)
  - [ ] Token in Zustand store (check React DevTools)

- [ ] **Session Persistence**
  - [ ] Refresh page → still logged in
  - [ ] Close and reopen browser → still logged in
  - [ ] Multiple tabs → session synced

- [ ] **Token Refresh**
